column5: Hey guys just wondering if anyone has been to Port Albert resintly for some Steelies? Are they in there yet? Doing my hunting course this weekend but would love to get out soon.
no fish or water, you could cross that river with out getting your feet wet
Even at the mouth? What about Goderich?
Was at Goderich Sunday.  Water is still on the low side and clear.
these guys are lying ...trust me on this .steelhead are in but action could get better
albert, godrich are hard to fish when it's verylow

well i think that if u have been there  in the last 5 days u would know that i,m not lying, but hey check it for yourself,ive fished this river for over 25 years and sun i seen the bottom of a hole that ive never seen??????????????????????
